{"tid":2414741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★食環鎖熟食中心防煙門　集中登記安心出行　涉違消防條例","createTime":"2021-02-19T15:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T11:34:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"14e82e025b8d3afc5191781996b820681c1eab2a","tid":2414741,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"大埔墟街市及熟食中心有走火通道的防煙門被食環署以鐵鏈鎖上，令市民須經指定出入口掃描登記，此舉疑違反《消防條例》，發生火警時或會阻礙逃生。東網正向食環署及消防處查詢。<br />\n<br />\n有關熟食中心位於大埔墟街市2樓，市民除正門外，可從熟食中心的載貨電梯大堂出入，熟食中心內另有走火樓梯往地面，但載貨電梯大堂的防煙門目前被食環署鎖上，而兩道出入熟食中心的防煙門，其中一道被食環署以鐵鏈鎖上，再以膠帶圍封，另一道門則有職員為進出市民登記及量度體溫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210219/bkn-20210219221728052-0219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210219%2Fbkn-20210219221728052-0219_00822_001.html&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGlKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=15a47434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210219/bkn-20210219221728052-0219_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6c84757e3927ec84d48bbc4a0db7237231bfa35","tid":2414741,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8456cb17ed7e6e485cbcfa98e725157320ce0406","tid":2414741,"uid":47810,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"燒死曬又真係唔怕病毒傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe10655c6d094312fd71bd349857545396f1ddac","tid":2414741,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"99e471d5382a405ce3f0a28b98a7b0acdee92ce2","tid":2414741,"uid